properties.name: Stretching our legs
properties.description: Just a quick break to rest our bums and stare at the ocean.

properties.name: Brick factory
properties.description: We helped stack the freshly pressed clay bricks.

properties.name: Minority village
properties.description: We gave candy to kids and learned about their language, school, and clothing.

properties.name: Bamboo farm
properties.description: This farmer was so friendly, showing us around and his wife invited us in for tea.

properties.name: Peppercorn farm
properties.description: We tasted the peppercorn right off the vine.

properties.name: Bees and rubber tree
properties.description: We tasted honey straight out of the hive and poked at the big chunks of rubber laying around.

properties.name: Banana leaf cakes
properties.description: We visited a house where the family was making Christmas cakes. It's a sticky rice with pork inside.

properties.name: Rice farmer
properties.description: The rice farmer was flattening mud in a field to prepare for planting.

properties.name: End of the tour :(
properties.description: After three wonderful days, Ut and Bom dropped us off at our hostel in Nha Trang.
